title: Whitney Wolfe Herd at Code 2023
summary:
Bumble Founder and CEO Whitney Wolfe Herd speaks with CNBC Correspondent Julia Boorstin at Code 2023. They discuss the power of AI, and whether it could play the role of a digital matchmaker.
Recorded on September 26th in Los Angeles.
